page.title: 01Montacute Somerset
page.content:
{ Montacute Service Station} Montacute Service Station is owned by Mr. P.L. Warry and Sons. It is situated on the outskirts of Montacute on the Yeovil Road and is open seven days a week selling petrol and a wide selection of cars and accessories. { {Stax} Stax is a fashion shop owned by Mr.Hann. It is situated on the corner of Townsend and sells a wide range of clothes and footwear. { {Stanley Roberts Manufacturing Agents} Stanley Roberts Manufacturing Agents is owned by Mr. N. Hann.It is situated in Townsend and is a manufacturing agent supplying mostly the Gloving Industry.
